OL,3,CCouncillors vote unanimously in favour
OL,4,Cof supporting tourism tax
OL,6,FPlans to introduce a tourism tax in
OL,7,FBath have moved a step closer after
OL,8,Fcouncillors voted unanimously in
OL,9,Fsupport of it.
OL,11,FCouncillors at Bath and North East
OL,12,FSomerset Council voted in favour of
OL,13,Fbeing able to introduce a tourism tax
OL,14,Fduring a meeting on 17 July.
OL,16,FThe vote was in support of the
OL,17,Fprinciple of a tax, not on actually
OL,18,Fintroducing one or how it would work.
OL,20,FBut what is a tourism tax and why is
OL,21,Fit being voted on?
