OL,6,FWhat is a tourism tax?
OL,8,FA tourism tax is a levy on short-stay
OL,9,Faccommodation in a local authority
OL,10,Farea.
OL,12,FAlso known as a 'transient visitor
OL,13,Flevy', a tax of this kind gives local
OL,14,Fcouncils the chance to charge people
OL,15,Fvisiting the area.
OL,17,FThe tax has been introduced in cities
OL,18,Fwith significant tourism economies
OL,19,Facross the world including Amsterdam,
OL,20,FBarcelona, and Vancouver.
