OL,11,FWhat are councillors in Bath and North
OL,12,FEast Somerset voting on?
OL,14,FCouncils in England do not yet have
OL,15,Fthe power to introduce such a measure
OL,16,Fbut authorities in Scotland do after
OL,17,Fthe Visitor Levy (Scotland) Act 2024
OL,18,Fwas passed last year.
