OL,3,CCouncillors vote unanimously in favour
OL,4,Cof supporting tourism tax
OL,6,FBath and North East Somerset Council
OL,7,Fleader, Kevin Guy, has written to
OL,8,Flocal government secretary Angela
OL,9,FRayner urging the government to give
OL,10,FEngland's historic cities the same
OL,11,Fpower.
OL,13,FMr Guy (Bathavon North, Liberal
OL,14,FDemocrat) said in a council meeting:
OL,15,F"We are not acting along and all we
OL,16,Fare doing is asking is for the
OL,17,Fgovernment to give us a fair deal
OL,18,Fbecause, at the moment, English cities
OL,19,Fare being short changed."
