OL,6,FHow would a tourism tax work?
OL,8,FA tourism tax is expected to take the
OL,9,Fform of an additional charge on
OL,10,Fovernight stays paid by the visitor to
OL,11,Fthe local council.
OL,13,FThe letter from Mr Guy and the leader
OL,14,Fof Cambridge City Council to the
OL,15,Fgovernment spoke of "a tourist levy
OL,16,Fassociated with overnight stays."
