OL,3,CCouncillors vote unanimously in favour
OL,4,Cof supporting tourism tax
OL,6,FThe letter states: "The revenue
OL,7,Fgenerated could be reinvested into the
OL,8,Fcommunity, improving facilities and
OL,9,Fservices for both residents and
OL,10,Fvisitors."
OL,12,FMr Guy said: "Any levy should apply
OL,13,Ffairly across all types of
OL,14,Faccommodation, including short-term
OL,15,Flets such as Airbnb."
OL,17,FSome supporters say it would help fund
OL,18,Finfrastructure and local services in
OL,19,Ftourist hotspots, including the upkeep
OL,20,Fof footpaths, public toilets, and
OL,21,Fwaste collections.
